summary: Okay but going by the fact that they’re all going after Thanos at what is obviously the start of the movie, and only a short...
body:
Okay but going by the fact that they’re all going after Thanos at what is obviously the start of the movie, and only a short time following the end of Infinity War, and Carol is with them.

Yet in the Quantum Realm suits scene, and pretty much every other scene featuring Natasha with red hair, aka a long time after the opening sequence, Carol isn’t in any of them, is anyone else very very very very very worried that Thanos is going to kill Carol or something???

Cause like, why isn’t she in any of those scenes?? It doesn’t make sense and it also makes me very very very nervous. Because even if it’s undone at the end, which it obviously would be if the time travel theory is true, I still would very much prefer NOT seeing Thanos kill Carol okay….
